text: Joonas Donskoi (born 13 April 1992) is a Finnish professional ice hockey forward. He currently plays for the Seattle Kraken of the National Hockey League (NHL). He has also played for the San Jose Sharks and Colorado Avalanche. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish ice hockey right wingers Category:Seattle Kraken players Category:San Jose Sharks players Category:Colorado Avalanche players
